        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>So, more gamemodes, more fun, I know that this probably won’t happen until the playerbase expands, but it’s fun to theory craft.</p>
<p>20 Players</p>
<p>Class List:<br>
1 King (60% BD, 10% Neut, 30% Psycho)<br>
1 Prince<br>
1 Reaper<br>
1 Sorcerer<br>
1 Possessor<br>
1 Inquisitor<br>
1 to 4 Other Neutrals<br>
11 to 13 Blue Dragon</p>
<p>No Unseen, No Cult, No Sheriff, No Paladin</p>
<p>Instead, Add in the Maid and the Squire from foL so that Maid can do “compatibility checks” and Squire can train.</p>
<p>Lots of killing, but no conversion.</p>
<p>Win Conditions:</p>
<p>BD: Kill all Neutral Killers<br>
Reaper, Possessor, Sorcerer, kill Blue Dragon<br>
Inquisitor: Personally kill or be the first accuser for at least One Neutral Killer</p>
<p>Magic Users: All NK, Psychic, Court Wizard</p>
